# DM Cvent Integration - Restart After Changes

When editing files in this project (app.py, templates, .env, etc.), **always restart the Flask app** after making changes so the user can test the updates.

Restart command:
```bash
kill -9 $(lsof -ti:5001) 2>/dev/null; sleep 2; cd "/Users/tga/Cursor/DM Cvent Integration" && python3 app.py
```
Run in background. The app runs on http://127.0.0.1:5001
